# /opt/etc/mihomo/devices.list — devices whose traffic goes through the VPN.
# One entry per line: a MAC address or an IP (optionally with /CIDR).
# Everything after the entry is a free-form comment.
# Manage with:  te-vpn add <mac|ip> [comment]   /   te-vpn remove <mac|ip>
#
# Examples:
#   aa:bb:cc:dd:ee:ff   laptop
#   192.168.1.50        tv
#   192.168.1.64/28     iot segment
